title: VonZipper : SIN : Fulton
description:
Shift Into Neutral

Truth be told, VZ has the hots for Mother Nature... So much in fact, we hug trees on a daily basis. It's with that embrace in mind; we're launching Shift Into Neutral -- a collection of sunglasses that are made from the environmentally friendly and sustainable materials.
